        "url": "/case-study/thumbtack",
        "title": "Thumbtack",
        "lastModifiedAt": 1778824528188,
        "htmlId": "articles--thumbtack--132d0e9faa",
        "sectionRelativeRepoPath": "thumbtack.md",
        "meta": {
          "category": "case study",
          "articleTitle": "Thumbtack migrates more than 90% of Macs with no IT intervention",
          "description": "Thumbtack migrated more than 90% of Macs to Fleet with no IT intervention and now manages devices with GitOps and fast Slack support.",
          "publishedOn": "2026-03-13",
          "authorGitHubUsername": "n/a",
          "authorFullName": "Fleetdm",
          "companyLogoFilename": "thumbtack-logo-197x40@2x.png",
          "quoteAuthorImageFilename": "adam-anklewicz-120x120@2x.png",
          "quoteAuthorName": "Adam Anklewicz",
          "quoteAuthorJobTitle": "Manager, IT Endpoint Engineering, Thumbtack",
          "quoteContent": "With Fleet, I just post something in our joint Slack channel and within minutes I will get a reply and we can have a proper conversation. Their support is huge — it's a big selling point for us.",
          "companyName": "Thumbtack",
          "companyInfo": "Thumbtack helps homeowners care for and improve their homes by connecting them with local service professionals. Through its platform, people get guidance on what projects to do, when to do them, and who to hire from a community of more than 300,000 service businesses across the United States.",
          "summaryChallenge": "Thumbtack needed a device management partner that could move at the same pace as its engineering team. Their existing Mac MDM relied on slow, ticket-based support, which delayed feedback and limited their ability to ship changes quickly. They also needed stronger CI/CD integration and a platform that could support infrastructure-as-code workflows.",
          "summarySolution": "After evaluating several vendors, Thumbtack selected Fleet. Fleet offered mature Apple MDM support, strong infrastructure-as-code capabilities, and a proven track record backed by customer references. With Fleet, Thumbtack gained a device management platform that integrates with its engineering workflows and supports faster iteration.",
          "summaryKeyResults": "Migrated more than 90% of Macs with no IT intervention.; Received fast, direct support during the migration, which increased confidence in the rollout.; Aligned endpoint management with existing GitOps workflows used across the engineering team.; Gained transparency by reviewing Fleet’s open source code and documentation."
        }
      },
