        "notes": "",
        "examples": "This table exposes all Docker labels on running containers. By joining it to\nthe [docker_containers](https://fleetdm.com/tables/docker_containers)table, we\ncan list containers and their maintainers.\n\n```\nSELECT dl.value, dc.name, FROM docker_container_labels dl JOIN docker_containers dc ON dl.id = dc.id WHERE key='maintainer';\n```",
