      {
        "name": "keychain_items",
        "description": "Generic details about keychain items. NOTE: osquery limits frequent access to keychain files. This limit is controlled by keychain_access_interval flag.",
        "url": "https://fleetdm.com/tables/keychain_items",
        "platforms": [
          "darwin"
        ],
        "evented": false,
        "cacheable": false,
        "notes": "- This table should be used sparingly as it uses an [Apple API which occasionally corrupts the underlying certificate](https://github.com/fleetdm/fleet/issues/13065#issuecomment-1658849614).",
        "examples": "Identify Macs that contain certificates related to Apple application signing\nand notarization. (replace with your Apple Developer ID string)\n\n```\nSELECT * FROM keychain_items WHERE label LIKE '%8EHZ83LZNU%';\n```",
