        "cacheable": true,
        "notes": "- `bssid` and `country code` are only available for macOS 11 and earlier because they would enable geolocation. ",
        "examples": "See the current speed of the WiFi connection, in megabits per second.\n\n```\nSELECT transmit_rate FROM wifi_status;\n```",
        "columns": [
